         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 8/9/73 ¶  ¶ I was glad to learn, dear Baron Cesati, that the Todea reached you safely, ¶  and trust that under your able care it will reestablish itself fully. ¶  ¶ As you enquire about ac...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">73.09.08</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Vincenzo Cesati</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Lettres et autographes d'Edm. Boissier et de William Barbey, Conservatoire et Jardin botanique, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS stamped 'ex COLL CESATI'.</p>
               </note>Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">8/9/73</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I was glad to learn, dear Baron Cesati, that the <name key="Todea">Todea</name> reached you safely,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">At Naples, Italy.</p>
               </note> and trust that under your able care it will reestablish itself fully.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As you enquire about acotyledonar plants, I would mention, that I should be happy to <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">send you any from here</hi>
               </seg> and consult you especially on many fungi, as you have worked on them so long and so gloriously. Will you kindly inform me, <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">in what manner</hi>
               </seg> I can serve you best. As the Cotyledonar plants of Australia will be brought to a close in the 7th vol next year,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The sixth volume of Bentham (1863-78) was published on 23 September 1873 but the final volume was delayed until March 1878 (TL2). Bentham gave priority to completing vol. 2, part 2, of Bentham &amp; Hooker (1862-83), which appeared in May 1876 (TL2); see for example G. Bentham to M, 9 September 1874 (in this edition as 74-09-09a), and G. Bentham to M, 23 August 1875.</p>
               </note> I intend to devote 2 or 3 years specially to the study of the Australian Agamous plants. I have however examined already all Filices and allied plants (about 200 species) carefully.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Can you shed any light on Tenore's Genus <name key="Donzellia">Donzellia</name>?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With regardful salutation,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>dear Baron,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The <name key="Todea">Todea</name> was entirely a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">private</hi>
               </seg> donation of my own; so you are under no obligation for it to the Government here.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Donzellia">Donzellia</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Todea">Todea</name>
            </p>
         </div>
